## 5 Non-Negotiable Strategic Constraints

1. **Strategic Decision 0 Option B** — Information + Tool + Decision Support ONLY. NEVER 추천/권장/비중 X%/지금 매수/timing입니다 / dashboard defer.
2. **Mobile-first PWA strict** — Tailwind mobile-first, vertical stack, 44px+ touch, bottom-fixed CTA, manifest+SW required.
3. **Dual mascot safety filter 3-layer (bidirectional)** — Layer 1 regex + Layer 2 Haiku classifier + Layer 3 redirect. All Claude API calls (Aurora + Vesper) pass through. Bidirectional (input + output) per Day 11 (commit 309f6ca).
4. **PIPA compliance strict** — Onboarding consent + Supabase RLS + 즉시 삭제 + Privacy/ToS before W5 launch. Q2 portfolio composition `JSONB` % 비율만 (절대 금액 X).
5. **Sprint 0 5-week cap** — V1 = Shape A polish + Shape C build (Behavioral Guard) + Aurora chat evolution + Toss live + Viral Option A + Layer 1 Opus daily cache + Daily Archive View. V2 explicitly deferred.

